t it according to your needs<br>        dev:<br>            pattern: ^/(_(profiler|wdt)|css|images|js)/<br>            security: false<br><br>        main:<br>            anonymous: ~<br>            guard:<br>                authenticators:<br>                    - app.form_login_authenticator<br>            logout:<br>                path: /logout<br>                target: /<br></pre><p></p><p>snapshot of error-:                              <a href="http://disq.us/url?url=http%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.org%2Fimage%2F52qvou1ox%2F%3A50VbC9-gI_ibEGeEB9iJfYkJuiQ&amp;cuid=1175718" rel="nofollow noopener">http://postimg.org/image/52qvo...</a><br>security.yml for (FOS) #pre1               <a href="http://disq.us/url?url=http%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.org%2Fimage%2Fmil1qj0nl%2F%3AdqxcxCTQYuR7ZnC1zAa5iyXTwJk&amp;cuid=1175718" rel="nofollow noopener">http://postimg.org/image/mil1q...</a><br>security.yml for #pre 2                         <a href="http://disq.us/url?url=http%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.org%2Fimage%2Ffe38hhte9%2F%3AHBCzBAlSy01_xBIRlcNTAT7u5ow&amp;cuid=1175718" rel="nofollow noopener">http://postimg.org/image/fe38h...</a></p>
