	                        <div id="dsq-comment-message-2549432666" class="dsq-comment-message">
	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2549432666" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>Hi Sudhir!</p><p>Ha, I like your "but but but" :). Your code mostly looks ok. But, you're missing the file_get_contents:</p><p><code><pre>$xml = file_get_contents($this-&gt;get('kernel')-&gt;getRootDir().'/../web/book.xml');<br></pre></code></p><p>Also, it probably doesn't matter (I'm guessing you're on windows?) - but use the forward slash (/) instead of (\) - the / will work even on Windows. And ultimately, do a `dump($xml);die;` to make sure that it actually is loading your XML. I think it's just not being loaded from the file.</p><p>Cheers!</p>
	                            </div>
